### resolver_input
<@&10> => [2, 3, 4]
<@&20> => [4, 5]
### source
core := <@&10> <@5>
<@1> paid 8400 to core
<@6> paid 3600 to <@2> <@3> <@4>
!member set <@5> cash
!settleup core --cash <@5> <@6>
### ast
L1 declaration core members=[<@5>] roles=[<@&10>] groups=[]
L2 payment amount=8400 payer=(members=[<@1>] roles=[] groups=[]) payee=(members=[] roles=[] groups=[core]) allocation=even
L3 payment amount=3600 payer=(members=[<@6>] roles=[] groups=[]) payee=(members=[<@2>, <@3>, <@4>] roles=[] groups=[]) allocation=even
L4 command !member set cash members=(members=[<@5>] roles=[] groups=[])
L5 command !settleup members=(members=[] roles=[] groups=[core]) cash=(members=[<@5>, <@6>] roles=[] groups=[])
